<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>Xác thực tài khoản</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            background: #FFFEF5;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #3a3a3a;
        }
        table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
            width: 100%;
        }
        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 580px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(45, 157, 217, 0.12);
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        /* header gradient mint sang coral */
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4ECDC4 0%, #FF6B6B 100%);
            padding: 70px 40px 50px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: #ffffff;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 70px 40px;
        }
        /* greeting màu sky blue */
        .greeting {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: #2D9DD9;
            margin: 0 0 35px 0;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .description {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #5a5a5a;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin: 0 0 32px 0;
        }
        /* highlight màu coral */
        .highlight {
            color: #FF6B6B;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }
        .code-section {
            margin: 60px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        /* code-label màu sky blue */
        .code-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #2D9DD9;
            letter-spacing: 2.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            display: block;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        /* code-box background gradient mint nhạt */
        .code-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E0F7F4 0%, #F0FFFE 100%);
            border: 2px solid #4ECDC4;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            margin: 0;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(78, 205, 196, 0.15);
        }
        .code-box::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FFD700 0%, #2D9DD9 100%);
            border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
        }
        /* code màu sky blue */
        .code {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2D9DD9;
            letter-spacing: 6px;
            word-break: break-all;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        /* divider gradient mint sang coral */
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #4ECDC4, transparent);
            margin: 50px 0;
        }
        /* info-section background gradient mint nhạt */
        .info-section {
            margin: 50px 0;
            padding: 35px 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E0F7F4 0%, #F0FFFE 100%);
            border-left: 5px solid #4ECDC4;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(78, 205, 196, 0.12);
        }
        /* info-title màu mint green */
        .info-title {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #4ECDC4;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .info-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #444444;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .verification-steps {
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        .step {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }
        /* step-number background màu sky blue */
        .step-number {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #2D9DD9;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-right: 18px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(45, 157, 217, 0.3);
        }
        .step-content {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #5a5a5a;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding-top: 4px;
        }
        /* expiry-notice background coral nhạt */
        .expiry-notice {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFE8E0 0%, #FFEDD5 100%);
            border-left: 5px solid #FF6B6B;
            padding: 30px 35px;
            margin: 50px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #4a4a4a;
            line-height: 1.9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.12);
        }
        /* support-link màu sky blue */
        .support-link {
            color: #2D9DD9;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #FF6B6B;
        }
        .support-link:hover {
            color: #FF6B6B;
            border-bottom-color: #2D9DD9;
        }
        /* footer gradient mint sang sky blue */
        .footer {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E0F7F4 0%, #E8F8FC 100%);
            padding: 60px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 2px solid #4ECDC4;
            border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
        }
        /* footer-text màu sky blue */
        .footer-text {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #2D9DD9;
            margin: 0 0 12px 0;
            line-height: 1.9;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .footer-divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #FFD700, transparent);
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .social-links {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        /* social-link màu mint green */
        .social-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 18px;
            color: #4ECDC4;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 12px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .social-link:hover {
            color: #FF6B6B;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 50px 25px;
            }
            .header {
                padding: 50px 25px 40px;
            }
            .greeting {
                font-size: 22px;
            }
            .description {
                font-size: 14px;
            }
            .code {
                font-size: 20px;
                letter-spacing: 5px;
            }
            .code-box {
                padding: 35px 25px;
            }
            .footer {
                padding: 50px 25px;
            }
            .info-section {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <table role="presentation">
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 30px 10px;">
                <table role="presentation" class="container">
                    <tr>
                        <td class="header">
                            <div class="logo">{{brandName}}</div>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="content">
                            <p class="greeting">Chào mừng {{userName}},</p>
                            <p class="description">
                                Cảm ơn bạn đã đăng ký tài khoản! Để hoàn tất quá trình xác thực, vui lòng nhập mã bên dưới.
                            </p>
                            <div class="code-section">
                                <span class="code-label">Mã xác thực email của bạn</span>
                                <div class="code-box">
                                    <p class="code">{{verificationCode}}</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="divider"></div>
                            <div class="verification-steps">
                                <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #2D9DD9; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 30px; font-weight: 700;">Hướng dẫn xác thực</p>
                                <div class="step">
                                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                                    <div class="step-content">
                                        Trở lại ứng dụng và nhập mã xác thực <span class="highlight">{{verificationCode}}</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="step">
                                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                                    <div class="step-content">
                                        Nhấn nút "Xác thực" để hoàn tất đăng ký
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="step">
                                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                                    <div class="step-content">
                                        Bắt đầu sử dụng tài khoản của bạn ngay lập tức
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="info-section">
                                <p class="info-title">Thông tin tài khoản</p>
                                <p class="info-text">
                                    Email: <strong>{{userEmail}}</strong><br>
                                    Thời gian xác thực hết hạn: <span class="highlight">10 phút</span>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="expiry-notice">
                                Mã này chỉ có hiệu lực trong <span class="highlight">10 phút</span>. Nếu bạn không yêu cầu xác thực, vui lòng bỏ qua email này.
                            </div>
                            <p class="description" style="text-align: center;">
                                Cần trợ giúp? Liên hệ với <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" class="support-link">đội hỗ trợ</a> của chúng tôi.
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="footer">
                            <p class="footer-text">
                                © {{year}} {{brandName}}. Bảo lưu mọi quyền.
                            </p>
                            <p class="footer-text">
                                {{companyAddress}}
                            </p>
                            <div class="footer-divider"></div>
                            <div class="social-links">
                                {{#if websiteUrl}}<a href="{{websiteUrl}}" class="social-link">Website</a>{{/if}}
                                {{#if twitterUrl}}<a href="{{twitterUrl}}" class="social-link">Twitter</a>{{/if}}
                                {{#if facebookUrl}}<a href="{{facebookUrl}}" class="social-link">Facebook</a>{{/if}}
                            </div>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
